<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>世界新闻头条、最新国际新闻、世界突发新闻 - 印度时报</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world</link><description>世界新闻：TOI 带来最新的世界新闻头条、《时事国际》全球突发新闻。深入分析和全球头条新闻。</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 16:08:22 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>俄罗斯秘密武器“托博尔”与干扰飞机信号有关</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/russias-secret-weapon-tobol-linked-to-jamming-of-planes-signals/articleshow/109531879.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109531879.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;波罗的海上空的商业航班受到俄罗斯武器“托博尔”的电子攻击，可能是为了保护军事设施。马丁·哈勒姆 (Martin Harem) 将军注意到 GPS 信号受到干扰。爱沙尼亚军事首长和《新闻周刊》报道了这些事件。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 11:15:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/russias-secret-weapon-tobol-linked-to-jamming-of-planes-signals/articleshow/109531879.cms</guid></item><item><title>“政策三难困境”：美国智库对普京和俄罗斯发出可怕警告</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/policy-trilemma-us-think-tanks-dire-warning-for-putin-russia/articleshow/109532244.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109532244.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;俄罗斯目前正面临政策“三难困境”，面临着为其军事行动提供资金、维持公民生活水平以及保持经济稳定的挑战，而这些目标越来越难以同时实现。根据卡内基国际和平基金会的预测，俄罗斯经济可能只能再维持目前的强劲势头 18 个月，然后就会开始陷入衰退。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 10:46:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/policy-trilemma-us-think-tanks-dire-warning-for-putin-russia/articleshow/109532244.cms</guid></item><item><title>Bavar-373：伊朗推出新武器系统对抗美国隐形飞机</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/bavar-373-iran-unveils-new-weapon-system-to-take-on-us-stealth-jets/articleshow/109531632.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109531632.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt; Bavar-373 系统于 2019 年首次投入使用，由于其功能，经常被与俄罗斯的 S-300 和美国制造的爱国者导弹系统进行比较。然而，据伊朗官员称，最新版本的 Bavar-373 据说甚至可以与俄罗斯更先进的 S-400 系统相媲美。在阅兵式上，Bavar-373 以其超过 186 英里的“令人印象深刻”的航程和高达 75 英里的高度而闻名。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 10:42:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/bavar-373-iran-unveils-new-weapon-system-to-take-on-us-stealth-jets/articleshow/109531632.cms</guid></item><item><title>亚历克·鲍德温在咖啡店冲突中打断反以色列抗议者手中的手机</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/alec-baldwin-smacks-phone-from-anti-israel-protesters-hand-in-coffee-shop-clash/articleshow/109530947.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109530947.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;视频记录了演员亚历克·鲍德温在咖啡店与一名反以色列抗议者发生冲突。支持巴勒斯坦的大学抗议活动促使警方介入耶鲁大学、哥伦比亚大学和纽约大学校园。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 10:17:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/alec-baldwin-smacks-phone-from-anti-israel-protesters-hand-in-coffee-shop-clash/articleshow/109530947.cms</guid></item><item><title>韩国因杀害76只猫被判入狱14个月</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/south-korean-sentenced-to-14-months-in-jail-for-killing-76-cats/articleshow/109530746.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109530746.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;一名来自韩国的年轻人因残忍杀害 76 只猫而被判处 14 个月监禁，这在韩国是一起令人不安的虐待动物案件。根据韩国东南部地区昌原地方法院的说法，这名 20 多岁的人被判犯有违反韩国动物保护法的罪行。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 10:12:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/south-korean-sentenced-to-14-months-in-jail-for-killing-76-cats/articleshow/109530746.cms</guid></item><item><title>法官将考虑在特朗普封口费审判中违反禁言令</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/judge-to-consider-gag-order-violations-in-trump-hush-money-trial/articleshow/109530418.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109530418.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;负责唐纳德·特朗普刑事封口费审判的法官将于周二决定这位美国前总统是否应该因违反禁止他批评该案证人的禁言令而面临后果。检察官要求对特朗普针对潜在证人斯托米·丹尼尔斯和迈克尔·科恩的言论处以罚款。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 10:07:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/judge-to-consider-gag-order-violations-in-trump-hush-money-trial/articleshow/109530418.cms</guid></item><item><title>候任总统：美国对台80亿美元军事援助计划将“增强地区信心”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/8-billion-us-military-aid-package-to-taiwan-will-boost-confidence-in-region-president-elect/articleshow/109530128.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109530128.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;台湾当选总统赖清德表示，美国众议院批准了一项价值 80 亿美元的国防计划，旨在增强西太平洋盟友链的威慑力。他强调，这笔资金将促进台海和平与稳定，并增强地区信心。赖在台北与密歇根州众议员丽莎·麦克莱恩和丹·基尔迪会面时传达了这一点。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 10:02:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/8-billion-us-military-aid-package-to-taiwan-will-boost-confidence-in-region-president-elect/articleshow/109530128.cms</guid></item><item><title>联合国人权事务高级专员对加沙医院乱葬坑的报道感到“震惊”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/un-rights-chief-horrified-by-mass-grave-reports-at-gaza-hospitals/articleshow/109529190.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109529190.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;据发言人称，联合国人权事务高级专员沃尔克·特克对加沙纳赛尔和阿尔希法医疗设施遭到破坏以及有报道称存在数百具尸体的乱葬坑表示震惊。巴勒斯坦当局在汗尤尼斯的一家医院被以色列军队遗弃后，在乱葬坑中发现了尸体。以色列特种部队行动后，希法基地也出现了类似的报道。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 09:40:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/un-rights-chief-horrified-by-mass-grave-reports-at-gaza-hospitals/articleshow/109529190.cms</guid></item><item><title>北约和俄罗斯即将进行核摊牌吗？</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/are-nato-and-russia-heading-for-nuclear-showdown/articleshow/109529084.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109529084.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;波兰准备拥有核武器以应对北约与俄罗斯的紧张局势，这凸显了与美国就加强安全问题进行更广泛的讨论。与此同时，美国参议院将就对乌克兰、以色列和台湾的重大战争援助进行投票。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 09:36:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/are-nato-and-russia-heading-for-nuclear-showdown/articleshow/109529084.cms</guid></item><item><title>中国猛烈抨击美国煽动乌克兰战争的说法“毫无根据”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/china-slams-groundless-us-claims-of-fuelling-ukraine-war/articleshow/109528083.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109528083.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;中国反驳美国关于在乌克兰援助俄罗斯的指控，强调中立。美国批评中国与俄罗斯的贸易，指责中国间接支持俄罗斯在乌克兰的军事行动。中国否认参与，坚称和平立场。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 09:08:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/china-slams-groundless-us-claims-of-fuelling-ukraine-war/articleshow/109528083.cms</guid></item><item><title>法国警方称至少有五名移民在试图穿越英吉利海峡时死亡</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/at-least-five-migrants-die-in-attempt-to-cross-english-channel-french-police-says/articleshow/109527784.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109527784.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;五名移民在维姆勒附近的英吉利海峡渡口死亡。英国立法允许将寻求庇护者送往卢旺达。许多移民冒着危险的海峡旅程到达英国海岸。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 08:53:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/at-least-five-migrants-die-in-attempt-to-cross-english-channel-french-police-says/articleshow/109527784.cms</guid></item><item><title>美军司令：中国在该地区正迅速变得更加咄咄逼人</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/us-commander-china-is-fast-becoming-more-aggressive-in-region/articleshow/109527123.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109527123.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;即将离任的美国印太司令部司令约翰·阿奎利诺海军上将周二在东京警告说，中国正在整个亚洲迅速升级其侵略立场和行为。在此之际，北京加大了对华盛顿的压力，恰逢国务卿托尼·布林肯即将对该国进行高风险访问。阿奎利诺强调，每个人都需要认识到中国前进的快速步伐。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 08:41:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/us-commander-china-is-fast-becoming-more-aggressive-in-region/articleshow/109527123.cms</guid></item><item><title>特朗普在封口费审判中被指控选举舞弊</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/trump-accused-of-election-fraud-in-hush-money-trial/articleshow/109519601.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109519601.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;特朗普因涉嫌向斯托米·丹尼尔斯支付封口费而面临 2016 年选举的审判。针对单独起诉的法律斗争仍在继续。检察官声称付款会影响选举结果。尽管面临越来越多的法律挑战，特朗普仍坚称自己无罪。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 07:13:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/trump-accused-of-election-fraud-in-hush-money-trial/articleshow/109519601.cms</guid></item><item><title>中国女子拍照时失足坠入印尼火山</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/chinese-woman-slips-into-indonesian-volcano-while-posing-for-photo-dies/articleshow/109523701.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109523701.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;黄丽红在伊真火山的惨死凸显了在火山附近拍摄的风险。由于印度尼西亚有 130 座活火山，Ruang 火山的喷发提醒人们要采取安全措施。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 07:07:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/chinese-woman-slips-into-indonesian-volcano-while-posing-for-photo-dies/articleshow/109523701.cms</guid></item><item><title>德国逮捕3名涉嫌中国间谍</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/germany-arrests-3-suspected-china-spies/articleshow/109519303.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109519303.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;德国国民因涉嫌通过获取军事技术协助中国间谍活动而被捕。该案例凸显了商业、工业和科学领域的风险。国际逮捕行动反映了人们对间谍活动日益增长的担忧，促使人们呼吁加强保护措施。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 05:12:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/germany-arrests-3-suspected-china-spies/articleshow/109519303.cms</guid></item><item><title>近东救济工程处：审查发现“中立”问题，没有证据证明恐怖</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/unrwa-review-finds-neutrality-issues-no-terror-proof/articleshow/109519615.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109519615.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 05:01:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/unrwa-review-finds-neutrality-issues-no-terror-proof/articleshow/109519615.cms</guid></item><item><title>马来西亚海军直升机空中相撞 10人死亡</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/10-dead-after-malaysian-navy-helicopters-collide-mid-air/articleshow/109518382.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109518382.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;海军报告称，在霹雳州北部的一个海军基地为即将到来的90周年庆典进行彩排时，发生了一起悲惨事件。事故涉及两架直升机，导致机上所有机组人员丧生。海军在一份简明声明中表示，“所有遇难者均被确认当场死亡”，并提到死者遗体已被运至医院进行身份识别。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 04:12:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/10-dead-after-malaysian-navy-helicopters-collide-mid-air/articleshow/109518382.cms</guid></item><item><title>印度裔已婚男子因殴打女友致死在新加坡被判入狱</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/nri/other-news/married-indian-origin-man-jailed-in-singapore-for-beating-girlfriend-to-death/articleshow/109517956.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109517956.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt; 40 岁的印度裔已婚男子 M Krishnan 周一因未构成谋杀其 40 岁女友 Mallika Begum Rahamansa Abdul Rahman 的过失杀人罪被判处 20 年监禁。2015 年，Krishnan 开始了婚外情。据新加坡法律观察报道，她与玛丽卡有染，玛丽卡在前几次婚姻中育有两个女儿。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 04:02:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/nri/other-news/married-indian-origin-man-jailed-in-singapore-for-beating-girlfriend-to-death/articleshow/109517956.cms</guid></item><item><title>警方称，闯入洛杉矶市长凯伦巴斯家的嫌疑人被捕</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/suspect-arrested-in-break-in-at-los-angeles-mayor-karen-basss-home-police-say/articleshow/109517323.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109517323.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 03:20:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/suspect-arrested-in-break-in-at-los-angeles-mayor-karen-basss-home-police-say/articleshow/109517323.cms</guid></item><item><title>台湾发生数十次地震但未造成重大损失</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/taiwan-rattled-by-dozens-of-quakes-but-no-major-damage/articleshow/109517290.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109517290.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt; 4月3日，人口稀少的花莲县发生7.2级地震，造成至少14人死亡，此后又发生了1000多次余震。台湾北部、东部和西部大部分地区（包括首都台北）的建筑物整夜摇晃，最大地震为 6.3 级。一切都很浅薄。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 03:18:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/taiwan-rattled-by-dozens-of-quakes-but-no-major-damage/articleshow/109517290.cms</guid></item></channel></rss>